    "description": "<strong> Visual Novel Sisters </strong> 是一个基于日本两姐妹故事的文字视觉故事。<br>这个游戏是一个讲故事的游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734890/extras/b6f5e625890a02c4b4bd35d7663db51d.avif?t=1747810464\" width=616 height=128 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >姐妹</h2><br>曾几何时，两姐妹住在同一地区。 老大是个美丽善良的姑娘，老三很生气。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734890/extras/c6b4dcbe34f22734063c3eb66c6101df.avif?t=1747810464\" width=616 height=128 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >山间旅行</h2>两姐妹决定去山上采橡子。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734890/extras/f353cc0fd95dea5e42ec21b7238d3a02.avif?t=1747810464\" width=616 height=128 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >奇怪的惊喜</h2>然而，一切都远非如此简单......在这个故事中，您将了解接下来发生的事情。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734890/extras/3e5b79c184ccd8027eb6ab238d699de2.avif?t=1747810464\" width=616 height=128 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 2 个女孩角色<br></li><li> 壮观的山区空间<br></li><li> 能够使用控件在空间中移动<br></li><li> 结局不寻常的叙事<br></li><li> 10 首主题音乐作品</li></ul>",
